Package edu.ncsu.csc216.garage.model.service_garage

Class ServiceBay

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.garage.model.service_garage.ServiceBay
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HybridElectricBay
    public class ServiceBay
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing a service bay in the garage. Service bays of this type are considered “regular,” and can handle both regular and hybrid/electric vehicles. The garage will start with 8 bays initially
    Author:
    Troy Boone

    • Constructor Detail

      • ServiceBay

        public ServiceBay()
        Default constructor. Creates a new empty service bay according to the current bay numbering, then increments that number. This bay accepts both hybrid and electric cars

      • ServiceBay

        public ServiceBay​(java.lang.String prefix)
        Alternative constructor. Creates a new empty service bay according to the current bay numbering and by attaching the prefix, then increments that number. This bay accepts both hybrid and electric cars
        Parameters:
        prefix - the beginning of the bay numbering
